<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ emailTitle }} - Password Reset Request</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #080D4A; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'; color: #4A5568; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<div style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 448px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden;">
        <div style="background-color: #7BBA29; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;">Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
            <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                To confirm your password reset request, please follow these steps:
            </p>
            <ol style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.125rem; list-style-type: decimal; list-style-position: inside; padding-left: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Use the temporary password provided:
                    <span style="font-weight: 700; color: #0045AD;">{{ currentPassword }}</span>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Click
                    <a href="{{ absolute_url('landing/login/link') ~ '?' ~ 'uuid=' ~ uuid|url_encode ~ '&verificationCode=' ~ verificationCode }}"
                       style="font-weight: 700; color: #7BBA29; text-decoration: underline;">here</a>
                    to proceed and validate your account.
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Log in using the temporary password, then set a new password.</li>
                <li>Download your OpenRoaming profile.</li>
            </ol>
            <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.125rem;">
                If you did not request a password reset, please contact the support team immediately.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #718096;">
                Support team:
                <a href="mailto:{{ contactEmail }}"
                   style="color: #0045AD; text-decoration: underline;">{{ contactEmail }}</a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #718096;">
                Thank you,<br>
                <strong>{{ emailTitle }} Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
